<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٣٠٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2891">صَدَقَةُ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3181">عَبْدُ الْحَمِيدِ بْنُ جُبَيْرِ بْنِ شَيْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيَّبِ </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5041">أُمَّ شَرِيكٍ </a>أَخْبَرَتْهُ: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أَمَرَهَا بِقَتْلِ الْأَوْزَاغِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>